cset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/chess-grandmaster-denies-cheating-in-new-interview-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/chess-grandmaster-denies-cheating-in-new-interview-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/chess-grandmaster-denies-cheating-in-new-interview-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/chess-grandmaster-denies-cheating-in-new-interview-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/chess-grandmaster-denies-cheating-in-new-interview-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/chess-grandmaster-denies-cheating-in-new-interview-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3505183" class="wp-caption-text">国际象棋棋盘 图片来源：Felix Mittermeier 来自 Unsplash</figcaption></figure><p>尼曼起诉了卡尔森和 Chess.com，以及特级大师和 Twitch 主播中村光 (Hikaru Nakamura)，后者还指控他在网站上作弊。</p><p>截至 8 月 28 日，这场价值 1 亿美元（7900 万英镑）的诽谤诉讼已达成和解，Chess.COM 恢复了尼曼的账户并允许他访问未来的赛事。</p><p>在摩根节目的采访中，主持人问他：“明确一点，关于具体指控——你在下棋时使用过肛珠吗？”</p><p>尼曼回答说：“嗯，你的好奇心有点令人担忧，你知道——也许你个人感兴趣，但我可以告诉你，不。断然地说，不，当然不是。” </p><figure id="attachment_3505184" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3505184" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3505184" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/chess-grandmaster-denies-cheating-in-new-interview.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/chess-grandmaster-denies-cheating-in-new-interview.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/chess-grandmaster-denies-cheating-in-new-interview-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/chess-grandmaster-denies-cheating-in-new-interview-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/chess-grandmaster-denies-cheating-in-new-interview-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/chess-grandmaster-denies-cheating-in-new-interview-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/chess-grandmaster-denies-cheating-in-new-interview-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3505184" class="wp-caption-text">国际象棋棋盘 图片来源：Damiano Lingauri 来自 Unsplash</figcaption></figure><p>为了强调他对粉碎这些指控的严肃态度，他去年<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-63010107" target="_blank" rel="noopener">表示</a>“如果他们想让我脱光衣服，我就会这么做”。</p><p> “我不在乎，因为我知道我很干净。你想让我在零电子传输的封闭盒子里玩，我不在乎。我来这里是为了获胜，无论如何这都是我的目标，”他继续说道。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/cd-projekt-red-3">CD Projekt Red</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/cyberpunk-2077"><em>《赛博朋克 2077》</em></a>中添加了一款受《毁灭战士》启发的<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/doom"><em>街机</em></a>游戏，重现了 Johnny Silverhand 从荒坂塔逃亡的场景。</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/chess-grandmaster-categorically-denies-using-vibrating-sex-toy-to-cheat-3505159">Chess grandmaster “categorically” denies using vibrating sex toy to cheat</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
